#~ "Unfortunately, they also introduced a regression that causes the "
#~ "<command>net</command> command to fail on many systems when querying "
#~ "remote hosts. If you experience this issue, you can add two lines to the "
#~ "[global] section of your <filename>smb.conf</filename> file to make "
#~ "browsing work again:"
